Moisturization: Shea butter is known for its intense moisturizing properties, helping to soothe and repair dry, chapped lips.

Long-Lasting Protection: Beeswax forms a protective barrier on the lips, sealing in moisture and protecting against harsh environmental conditions.

Rich in Vitamins: Almond oil is packed with Vitamin E, which is essential for skin health. It helps to nourish and soften lips, making them smooth and supple.

Antioxidant Power: Vitamin E oil is a powerful antioxidant that helps protect the lips from damage caused by free radicals, keeping them youthful and healthy.

The natural enzymes in papaya gently exfoliate dead skin cells, helping to reveal brighter, smoother skin and reduce the appearance of blemishes, tan, and dark spots. Its rich source of vitamins A, C, and E also promotes hydration and skin elasticity.

Green apple, loaded with antioxidants and essential nutrients, enhances the skin’s natural radiance and provides deep hydration. Its high vitamin C content boosts collagen production, making the skin firmer and more youthful. The fruit’s mild astringent properties also help control excess oil and reduce acne.

Together, these ingredients create a nourishing blend that cleanses, detoxifies, and brightens your skin, leaving it feeling soft, smooth, and rejuvenated. Suitable for all skin types, this soap offers a fruity, refreshing fragrance, perfect for a daily skincare routine.

title: Coffee Shampoo
description:
•	Coffee prevents hair loss:
The common cause of a male’s hair loss is derived from the effects of the male hormone dihydrotestosterone (DHT). DHT affects hair follicles and slowly creates baldness. When you apply caffeine, though, DHT is suppressed. Then caffeine stimulates hair roots so that hair follicles in an anagen growth phase are motivated to grow stronger, increasing their stamina and endurance.
•	Stimulate hair growth:
Caffeine is rich in antioxidants that block possible cause of cell damage and reduces transepidermal water loss (TDWL or TWL) and stimulate healthy cell production.

•	Coffee for hair growth to improve hair structure:
It’s no secret that regular use of caffeine strengthens hair follicles and its related cell structures so hair becomes softer.
•	Caffeine Stimulates Hair Matrix Keratinocyte Proliferation:
The hair matrix, where the hair shaft is produced, is a critical part of hair follicle anatomy. This hair matrix produces keratin, the major protein component of hair. Different clinical studies have shown that caffeine stimulates the proliferation of keratinocytes.

title: Moringa Shampoo
description:
Moringa Shampoo:
Moringa shampoo is a blend of moringa-leaf and various herbs formulated to protect and repair hair follicles, repair dead ends, and prevent hair fall. 
Here are some of the benefits of using moringa shampoo for hair loss: 
•	Puts a stop to hair fall: Moringa shampoo can help with this. Moringa is rich in Vitamin B and it contains Vitamin E which promotes a healthy nourished scalp.

•	Works well for dandruff and dry scalp: Dandruff and dry scalp is a common reason for hair loss. The presence of vitamins B, C, and E in the moringa shampoo helps to nourish roots and ultimately works to fight hair loss.
•	Slows down early graying: Gray hair is caused when the oxidation process in the body creates free radicals that cause damage to cells and strips away natural hair color. By consuming moringa and using moringa shampoo you can help slow down gray hairs.

title: Mega Clenz
description:
Mega Clenz floor cleaning liquid  is a water based unique formula with copper as main ingredient to kill all types of germs along with soft chemicals.
- Floor cleaner with preferred aroma.  (Lavender, Jasmine, Rose, Citrus, Lemon Grass) 

It is a High quality and High performance floor cleaner works against wide range of microorganisms  viz.,bacteria, fungal, virus, molds, spores etc., and kills 99.9% of germs in less than 60s.
fact:
Directions of Use:
1. Take approx. 16ml of the solution and add into 4L of water and  rinse thoroughly. 
2. Mop the surface with cloth or the liquid can be poured in the machine to clean the surface as well.
3. For stuff stains- take 10ml of Mega Clenz and apply directly on the stain and rub with a brush or cloth.   
4. Mega Clenz can be used on bathroom floors, and tiles as well In bathroom floor and tiles it can be poured directly to clean 
5. Mega Clenz can be used in floor cleaning machines.

title: Toilet Cleaning Liquid
description:
Loo Clenz’s (Toilet Cleaner) advanced formula penetrates and dissolves tough stains and mineral deposits, making it easy to achieve a spotless toilet bowl.

Our disinfecting agents effectively kill 99.9% of germs and bacteria, helping to prevent the spread of illness and keeping your bathroom clean and hygienic.
fact:
Direction of Use:

• Squeeze Loo Clenz around the rim of the toilet bowl

• Use a toilet brush to scrub inside of the bowl thoroughly, making sure to reach under the rim and around the edges where grime tends to accumulate

• Scrub until all surfaces are covered with the cleaner

• After the appropriate amount of time has passed, say around 3 minutes, flush the toilet to rinse away the cleaner and loosen grime

• Be sure flush or pour water multiple times until all the cleaner residue is removed

title: Bronze Harihara
description:
Harihara — Union of Vishnu and Shiva

A rare and powerful depiction of divine balance, Harihara merges two great cosmic forces Vishnu the preserver and Shiva the transformer into a single harmonious form.

One side holds the conch and chakra, the other the trident and damaru. Together, they represent unity beyond duality, a reminder that all divinity flows from one source.
